src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSame bro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我hd2年就係咁樣過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都唔知咁樣算唔算失眠 明明日頭咁撚好訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一開頭係真失眠 攤落床有各種狀況訓唔到<br />\n之後就諗既然都訓唔到 不如遲啲先上床啦<br />\n搞到而家都未訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日日訓得兩三粒鐘可想而之gpa可以有幾高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n比自己玩死"},{"pid":"a0ab2cf8287b59af28fdd7abca79da7532bb1a62","tid":225530,"uid":41745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T22:56:42.000Z","msg":"我都想訓呀"},{"pid":"c58b7d07b2780b306bdc8a0b2d399035aaf9e364","tid":225530,"uid":4824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T22:57:11.000Z","msg":"我琴日4點pm先起身 起身打左個丁 到依家想訓 <br />\n但又怕訓左又訓到6，7點 不停咁loop<br />\nBtw我琴日打左個丁丁依家無訓 會唔會出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dadc5ba21abe9f67819cf72e3a83876b30e14c39","tid":225530,"uid":83023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T22:58:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我琴日4點pm先起身 起身打左個丁 到依家想訓 <br />\n但又怕訓左又訓到6，7點 不停咁loop<br />\nBtw我琴日打左個丁丁依家無訓 會唔會出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打多幾次可能好訓啲"},{"pid":"bfb819bb344f0ac20193d5bb9a64c17c699e5304","tid":225530,"uid":4824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T22:59:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我琴日4點pm先起身 起身打左個丁 到依家想訓 <br />\n但又怕訓左又訓到6，7點 不停咁loop<br />\nBtw我琴日打左個丁丁依家無訓 會唔會出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打多幾次可能好訓啲</blockquote><br />\n我成日覺得打左丁再通頂會死得人<br />\n打多幾次？不了 我怕身體頂唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09ccb89de93cfd22dc6665ff331d50b14f1c4c47","tid":225530,"uid":49131,"like":0,"disli