ji\" />"},{"pid":"a279b5eb49ff765514634b31bea79ccd40768528","tid":225530,"uid":33653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T23:04:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每日唔到4 5 am 先覺得有睡意<br />\n一訓就4 5 pm 先醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n重要愈訓個人愈攰<br />\n結果不斷重複<br />\n有咩方法可以搞返好個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nme too"},{"pid":"dc3e6c6c5654cac6b15a230c0acadaf394dde0e7","tid":225530,"uid":11856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T23:05:12.000Z","msg":"睇錯心理時鐘"},{"pid":"df68f35d9f74c70f428ef0aa6e6886b1f67c2f75","tid":225530,"uid":96919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T23:05:41.000Z","msg":"明明好攰 但係又訓唔到嘅感覺 真係好攞命"},{"pid":"004da77e3d7be50c9e2b9e146e863dc79ea42378","tid":225530,"uid":11314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T23:06:47.000Z","msg":"依家去訓覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1abc5a6f0e85add8cf84c477f19064465412dbbe","tid":225530,"uid":74431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T23:07:59.000Z","msg":"其實睇你意志力<br />\n早起到就早起 涯唔到都無人幫到你<br />\n有時好簡單起床一件事 都要好大既覺悟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"968ab3cbcf7444d1cc2fa5f6cef29dbe528153be","tid":225530,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T23:08:46.000Z","msg":"我每朝先瞓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"418e5cc00523bb74d7dc0a67741e92746063b2ca","tid":225530,"uid":48645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T23:09:30.000Z","msg":"朝早十一二點 夜晚八九點起身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b151812e7b0aa9291ba723eeaedefde4c21f736","tid":225530,"uid":97