呢個世界<br />\n環境好<span style=\"color: red;\">靜</span>, <br />\n落街買野食無人, <br />\n行過d 商場無人sell你野, <br />\n入lift唔需要面對鄰居,<br />\n<br />\n簡單d 講, 就係毒撚時鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"b11a40571b0141e3cf1f280af5c10c08c011600f","tid":225530,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T23:47:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>關撚事，廢青冇工返有撚責任，有撚野管你起身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nAgger<br />\n我維持左幾個月一返工就無野"},{"pid":"39ce8ddf5c8a9c6a926b5994bc8319edf60dc7af","tid":225530,"uid":863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T23:48:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"27101abfeeb11d6aee349cb27c59cb81c9402f97","tid":225530,"uid":25052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T23:50:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌我都係<br />\n明明身體好攰 10點就攤落床 都要等到2點幾訓得著 但要6點起身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係咁 明明個身好攰 但一瞓落床就好精神瞓唔著 瞓到都係醒下瞓下咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9c3e7573ed6bcffe3d83c7585b65b9753888dac","tid":225530,"uid":81722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T23:50:13.000Z","msg":"心理時鐘亂哂"},{"pid":"9ef3d8780856aee0f716844916ddfb1e67d4952f","tid":225530,"uid":3098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T23:51:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一樣 而家做緊廢青 因為某d原因唔洗返學<br />\n7-8am訓 訓返12個鐘 7-8pm醒 有時可以訓到9pm <br />\n尋日食吉野家邊爐做早餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a0c3945fbebda7f712096358084eeeb86699c43","tid":225530,"uid":3427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T23:52:09.000Z","msg":"好似好傷"},{"pid":"961b368001b0d5736c616916d4b6ab4f1e6149fb","tid":225530,"uid":64225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T23:52:34.000Z","msg":"搵份夜