e":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T00:40:56.000Z","msg":"考完個dse就已經亂撚晒<br />\n琴晚12點終於訓到點知4點起左身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14c5cdaf3c40458cbcefd44056c5c39deeaad16e","tid":225530,"uid":61832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T00:43:54.000Z","msg":"唔好飲任何茶類飲品<br />\n連通2晚 唔好訓 但千祈唔好打機<br />\n打機會越打越精神<br />\n睇多d書<br />\n健康飲食 飲多d水<br />\n第2日夜晚10點就上床訓"},{"pid":"04ee4c6c88653473424dc2b089e0a81408594b0c","tid":225530,"uid":18559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T00:57:52.000Z","msg":"琴晚4點訓而家上堂好撚眼訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4520762a6dfedba770330b0b19f6687af3eb085","tid":225530,"uid":3434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T00:58:53.000Z","msg":"慣左返學早起身<br />\n依家放假12點半要訓 8點半起身<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8d7428de00a8b865ceee6ba5ef6ebfcd409be51","tid":225530,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T00:59:54.000Z","msg":"早啲撻落床瞓囉<br />\n一係搵一日唔好瞓，去到夜晚先瞓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddafb7b9590925cad7dda72bc1275cb0e58f0e6b","tid":225530,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T01:03:28.000Z","msg":"我要早上十點幾先開始眼訓<br />\n之後訓到中午4,5點起身<br />\n<br />\n利: <br />\n近一年無返全職 <br />\n唔係廢青 之前揾到 <br />\n唔返全職因為有特別原因"},{"pid":"dd422e63fc8521dd31b12196220201bf4b5647a8","tid":225530,"uid":43721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T01:11:09.000Z","msg":"假如琴日4點正訓<br />\n今晚開始3點45入睡<br />\n訓一至三晚 再早15分鐘<br />\n如此類推<br />\n過來人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過一次夜訓就會打回原形<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我而家都好夜訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6735b819aa7074b0f9dad67bbdcbcf67e5df845","tid":225530,"uid":66759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T01:12:03.000Z","msg":"一樣"},{"pid":"73c879058b03f246676d62675eb12d6b07fa663a","tid":225530,"uid":60651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T01:16:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">一心入黎睇橙色世界</span>"},{"pid":"8be4976a73f932725bb81c6ad88312721c142a24","tid":225530,"uid":41434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T01:19:05.000Z","msg":"平時1，2點訓<br />\n放長假就5，6點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但長假最尾果日會早唔到訓<br />\n即係今日咁琴晚4點訓好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb16c46812f1c933f6ce4e92e3bcb6a50fde4994","tid":225530,"uid":75198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T01:22:09.000Z","msg":"前排我都成三點幾先訓到<br />\n但依排做運動做到勁攰<br />\n玩玩下手機訓著左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e30c9e9b13bc4d4bf2cb49d76d187f5320f08121","tid":225530,"uid":35992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T01:25:01.000Z","msg":"食退黑激素喇，自己上網查下，唔係安眠藥"},{"pid":"4af32175892f7b16315b627e542e8614f47d9ed4","tid":225530,"uid":76804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T01:29:20.000Z","msg":"睇字都覺得傷身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我以前都試過晚晚三四點 試過六點先訓<br />\n諗番都覺得好癲<br />\n仲要係中學<br />\n後尾開始覺得傷身就12點訓"},{"pid":"6babb6ab658c3b0d25d3c90a469737f7e55e1d8b","tid":225530,"uid":76804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T01:30:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>假如琴日4點正訓<br />\n今晚開始3點45入睡<br />\n訓一至三晚 再早15分鐘<br />\n如此類推<br />\n過來人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過一次夜訓就會打回原形<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我而家都好夜訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係呀<br />\n夜一日就放縱自己<br />\n第二日就會諗 是旦啦夜訓無所謂<br />\n咁就不斷loop<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e5522c4120bd4d29da27b0e842c318807d98c01","tid":225530,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T01:35:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好飲任何茶類飲品<br />\n連通2晚 唔好訓 但千祈唔好打機<br />\n打機會越打越精神<br />\n睇多d書<br />\n健康飲食 飲多d水<br />\n第2日夜晚10點就上床訓</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fe433a7455a4996b9ec62728f9ef5739fff3791","tid":225530,"uid":50359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T01:39:52.000Z","msg":"係咪有飲開茶?<br />\n有啲人對咖啡因好敏感 飲杯奶茶都失眠<br />\n我果係呢啲人<br />\n唔好飲茶，通晚頂試下"},{"pid":"a38016ae1ae128eab64b282a09a81c3cad8ca151","tid":225530,"uid":2022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T01:44:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"79d08a807dd6cc2e78823a97646b3c407f95b02c","tid":225530,"uid":666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T01:45:44.000Z","msg":"根據當年做廢青經驗<br />\n死頂係頂唔到<br />\n<br />\n搵日搵d 野做, 臨訓set 個訓4粒鐘既鬧鐘起身<br />\n根住頂返到夜晚就差唔多又眼訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d496b13f9520ae415fb808bdda61aedf2592ac8","tid":225530,"uid":15083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T01:47:43.000Z","msg":"未訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f744d09fc988e976247f890fe5c7463b612cacb","tid":225530,"uid":40306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T01:55:44.000Z","msg":"me too<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92e0623e822642431dea7e1531a97bb09664de73","tid":225530,"uid":112379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T01:55:57.000Z","msg":"5點都未訓到 今朝740 起身翻學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\