y":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T02:37:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每日唔到4 5 am 先覺得有睡意<br />\n一訓就4 5 pm 先醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n重要愈訓個人愈攰<br />\n結果不斷重複<br />\n有咩方法可以搞返好個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99a7ae86a46f8676cfcb311e4194bf29fc018de6","tid":225530,"uid":67697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T02:53:23.000Z","msg":"無論琴晚幾夜訓都好，堅持第朝6-8am起身<br />\n吸下陽光，夜晚就好訓d<br />\n起唔到既就試下起身果下即刻開窗簾<br />\n被光照一照 抑制下d褪黑激素<br />\n<br />\n我就係成功人士喇<br />\n由2am訓教，用幾日就調返11pm訓"},{"pid":"64a8e3710530961771182c52cfb42634e42baa14","tid":225530,"uid":54834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T03:05:41.000Z","msg":"我都係<br />\n日日三四點先瞓到<br />\n前兩日要五六點先得<br />\n搞到差唔多一兩回先起身溫到書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依兩日飲咗少少酒先瞓<br />\n情況好少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce5bdd880061572cc768439777b624f7518d0910","tid":225530,"uid":51058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T03:27:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我每朝先瞓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83bf347dd0b267b58a8a5b95af2f5e8d8fc3d48a","tid":225530,"uid":79485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T03:32:59.000Z","msg":"仆野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bf3018821fc66ab99ff7152a2005a6683c5cbc1","tid":225530,"uid":16661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T03:42:57.000Z","msg":"我之前都5-7am先訓 <br />\n